# Analysis Scripts

This folder contains Python scripts that analyse
the AIDev dataset sample data.

## Scripts in Order

### 01_load_data.py
Loads the sample_prs.csv dataset and explains
every column. Shows what AIDev dataset looks like.

### 02_acceptance_rate.py
Calculates which agents get their PRs accepted.
Connects to Finding #2 from the AIDev paper.

### 03_library_check.py
Scans the patch column for import statements.
This is exactly what pr_commit_details analysis does.
Produces the 29.5% library import rate.

### 04_version_check.py
Checks requirements.txt changes for version numbers.
Produces the 1.3% and 75.0% findings.

## How to Run
```bash
python analysis/01_load_data.py
python analysis/02_acceptance_rate.py
python analysis/03_library_check.py
python analysis/04_version_check.py
```
